name: MIAdream
description:
It's a merge. Creates some interesting results. Can be used at 512x512 and 768x768. Based on 1.5.

~It's much less capable at making MIA related images than the original model, but the art style remains strong.

Seems to work well with story type prompts. Example: You find yourself standing on the edge of a vast, rolling ocean, with waves crashing against the shore. The sky above is a deep shade of purple, with swirling clouds that seem to dance and twirl in the wind.

As you take in the breathtaking view, you notice a faint glow on the horizon. As you watch, the glow grows brighter and more intense, until it is almost blinding. Suddenly, a bolt of lightning splits the sky, and you feel a jolt of electricity pass through your body.

You realize that you are standing in the midst of a powerful storm, with winds howling and rain lashing against your skin. You feel a sense of awe and wonder wash over you as you watch the storm rage on.

But as the winds pick up and the waves grow higher, you also feel a sense of danger. You know that you must find shelter, or risk being swept away by the powerful forces of nature. Do you brave the storm and search for shelter, or do you turn back and seek safety? The choice is yours.

______________________________

Note from creator(s) of MIA:


I recommend using the following always at beginning of your positive prompt: masterpiece, best quality;

I recommend using the following always as negative prompt: lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry

(These are NovelAI's prompt template settings)


PROMPT FORMAT: Character, tag1, tag2, etc; Character2, tag 1, tag2, etc; Location (this is the format the model is trained with, it's not necessary but recommended for best results)


explanation for this prompt format: Commas separate subtags for a major concept or character while semicolons act as major concept separators for generating multiple characters or marking the location at end of prompt.


EXAMPLES: 

masterpiece, best quality; Riko, shift dress, red whistle; orphanage

masterpiece, best quality; Riko, delver outfit, red whistle; Reg, aubade helmet, aubade cape, backpack; upper second layer

masterpiece, best quality; Riko, delver outfit, red whistle; Reg, aubade helmet, aubade cape, arm extended; lower second layer, seeker camp

masterpiece, best quality; Habo, black whistle; Reg, aubade cape; the first layer, eternal fortunes


If struggling to generate a character solo, try adding tags like "masterpiece, best quality, solo; Riko, shift dress, red whistle; orphanage"

meta.prompt:
As you stand in the aftermath of the nuclear explosion, you survey your new form. Your skin is now a shimmering, metallic silver, with intricate patterns and symbols etched into it. Your eyes seem to glow with an inner light, and you can feel a new strength and vitality coursing through your veins.
Your makeshift suit of armor has become a part of you, seamlessly blending with your skin to create a sleek and powerful appearance. You are now a being of extraordinary abilities, with enhanced strength, speed, and endurance. You feel ready to face any challenge that comes your way in this harsh and unforgiving world.
As you look around, you see the ruins of the city stretching out before you. The landscape is scarred and desolate, with twisted metal and broken concrete as far as the eye can see. But you are no longer afraid. You are a survivor, and you are determined to thrive in this new and dangerous world.

meta.prompt: A bandit wearing dystopian armor stands atop a crumbling skyscraper, surveying the chaos of the ravaged city below. In the distance, flames lick at the remains of a factory, while a group of rebels fights against a group of heavily armed soldiers. The bandit's face is shrouded in shadow, but the glint of their armor suggests they are not to be trifled with. In the background, a storm rages on, lightning illuminating the sky as the bandit contemplates their next move. The scene is captured in stunning 8k resolution, the intricate details of the armor and the destruction brought on by the dystopian world brought to life by the skilled hand of artist Eddy Li. The piece is rendered in Unreal Engine, adding to the hyper realistic feel of the scene. A true masterpiece, this image captures the essence of the chaotic and dangerous world of the dystopian bandit.
